ActCanadian Transportation Accident Investigation and Safety Board Act
PrecisAppointment of KATHLEEN CAROL FOX of Gatineau, Quebec, to be a full-time member of the Canadian Transportation Accident Investigation and Safety Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years; and designation of KATHLEEN CAROL FOX as Chairperson of the Board, effective August 21, 2014.
